OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FA scandal victim has said the
OL,8,Fgovernment is waiting for them to "die
OL,9,Foff" amid mounting concerns over the
OL,10,Feffectiveness of compensation payout.
OL,12,FConroy Downie, a 67-year-old Windrush
OL,13,Fvictim who has been advising thousands
OL,14,Fof others on how to make compensation
OL,15,Fclaims and is still waiting for his
OL,16,Fcase to be fully settled, said: "It's
OL,17,Fa failure, it's disgusting. I think
OL,18,Fthey are waiting for us to die off."
