OL,7,FThe great-grandfather, who was born in
OL,8,FJamaica and came to the UK as a
OL,9,Fteenager before joining the Army but
OL,10,Ftwice wrongly faced deportation amid
OL,11,Fthe scandal, said "the system has
OL,12,Ffailed us" as he described how one of
OL,13,Fthe main problems was that people
OL,14,Fstill "don't trust the Home Office".
