OL,3,CWindrush scandal: Compensation scheme
OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FThe compensation scheme has been in
OL,8,Fplace since April 3, 2019 in a bid to
OL,9,Fright the wrongs of the scandal, which
OL,10,Femerged a year earlier and saw many
OL,11,FBritish citizens, mostly from the
OL,12,FCaribbean, denied access to healthcare
OL,13,Fand benefits and threatened with
OL,14,Fdeportation despite having the right
OL,15,Fto live in the UK.
