OL,3,CWindrush scandal: Compensation scheme
OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FCritics of the beleaguered scheme have
OL,8,Frepeatedly called for the Home Office
OL,9,Fto be stripped of responsibility for
OL,10,Fdetermining and handling payments to
OL,11,Fvictims and said it should be turned
OL,12,Fover to an independent body instead.
OL,14,FDespite growing concerns around the
OL,15,Fnumber of people dying before
OL,16,Freceiving payouts, the Home Office has
OL,17,Fso far resisted demands for such
OL,18,Freforms, warning that changing how the
OL,19,Fsystem is administered could disrupt
OL,20,Fclaims being processed and lead to
OL,21,Fdelayed payments.
