OL,3,CWindrush scandal: Compensation scheme
OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FImmigration and human rights lawyer
OL,8,FJacqueline McKenzie, who has worked
OL,9,Fwith more than 400 Windrush victims,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Like the Post Office Horizon
OL,11,Fscandal, it is deplorable that the
OL,12,Fscheme is managed by the perpetrators
OL,13,Fof the wrong."
OL,15,FThe partner and head of immigration
OL,16,Fand asylum law at the firm Leigh Day
OL,17,Fsaid the Home Office "must speed up
OL,18,Fthe decision making" and work with
OL,19,Flawyers and campaigners to bring about
OL,20,Freform.
