OL,7,FWhile there have been "some
OL,8,Fimprovements" over the years, "we are
OL,9,Fstill some way to go to say the scheme
OL,10,Fis operating in an efficient way", she
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FThe comments follow calls last month
OL,14,Fin the Lords for Windrush scandal
OL,15,Fvictims to have similar support to
OL,16,Fthose affected by the Post Office
OL,17,Fscandal.
