OL,7,FAccording to analysis of the latest
OL,8,Favailable Home Office figures, 7,862
OL,9,Fclaims have been made as of January
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FA total of #80.1 million had been paid
OL,13,Fout by the end of the first month of
OL,14,Fthis year for 2,233 claims - an
OL,15,Faverage of nearly #35,900 per claim.
