OL,7,FMeanwhile just over a third (35%) of
OL,8,Fclaims in January 2024 had been in the
OL,9,Fsystem for one to three months, down
OL,10,Ffrom 39% a year earlier, but up from
OL,11,F18% two years ago in January 2022.
OL,13,FThe number of claims received by case
OL,14,Fworkers has been on a downward trend
OL,15,Fin recent months.
