OL,7,FThe average was 174 per month in the
OL,8,Fthree months to January 2024, down
OL,9,Ffrom 204 in the previous three months
OL,10,Fand well below the 286 per month in
OL,11,Fthe equivalent three months a year
OL,12,Fearlier (November 2022 to January
OL,13,F2023).
OL,15,FThe Home Office insisted the
OL,16,Fgovernment "remains absolutely
OL,17,Fcommitted to righting the wrongs of
OL,18,Fthe Windrush scandal" and has
OL,19,Fcontinued to improve the process so
OL,20,Fpeople "receive the maximum award as
OL,21,Fquickly as possible".
